### 1. Hardwareregistrierung und Onboarding
POST http://localhost:3000/api/admin/onboard
Content-Type: application/json
x-api-key: MASTER_ADMIN_2026

{
    "hardwareId": "ESP_001",
    "supplierName": "Lieferant1",
    "deliveryId": "SHIP-2026-001"
}

### 2. Definition der Limits
POST http://localhost:3000/api/admin/set-limit/Lieferant1/SHIP-2026-001
Content-Type: application/json
x-api-key: MASTER_ADMIN_2026

{
    "maxTemp": 24.0,
    "minTemp": 2.0,
    "maxHum": 60.0,
    "minHum": 20.0
}